version_description: None of the existing tabs have the Bb/C
Full and well-aligned chords for vocal and instrumental parts / tab for intro and chorus / suggestions for voicings.
The difference is that I use both Dsus4 and Dsus2 in the verses while others just use one of them and there are some other minor extra things
It differs from any previous versions.  I have confirmed from visual evidence, that it matches the original chords.
